Scenarios to be covered in Docker:

1) Installation of docker on standalone server.
2) Configuring Docker hub and playing with Images pull and push commands.
3) Configuring ECR AWS service instead of Docker hub.
4) Building a normal Tomcat application on docker.
5) Running applications like MYSQL, Mongo DB, PostreSQL kind of databases on docker.
6) Integrating different components of applications with different Docker Containers( Micro Services Concept ).
7) Docker Compose and docker build concept.


Kubernetes

1) Complete setup of kubernetes.
2) Understanding concepts like Pod, Services, Deployment and exposing service.
3) Setup using sample application on kubernetes.
4) Performing deployment with new Docker images file.
5) Rollback concept in case of Kubernetes.
